H0.text: Its color changed is a property of the cooking oil after it was poured into the container.

H1.text: Its mass increased is the property of the cooking oil after it was poured into the container.

H2.text: Its volume stayed the same is a property of the cooking oil after it was poured into the container.

H3.text: Its temperature quickly increased after liquid cooking oil was poured into a container.

A4.text: Liquids are nearly incompressible, maintaining their volume even under pressure.
